{"tid":379073,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人打機係成日輸:o)","createTime":"2017-08-29T03:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T16:19:06.000Z","uid":49524,"like":9,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88b697a413ff7a5647853a56902beeabc9f17d2f","tid":379073,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:44:54.000Z","msg":"以前細個玩彩虹冒險係場場都輸<br />\n之後任何槍game都射唔中人 行出去畀人爆頭就有<br />\n<br />\n到lol打左幾年 就算自己個場幾勁 carry左隊友<br />\n但最後到關鍵位都係輸我on9而輸返成局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n近來玩Splatoon2同Mario kart終於贏返多啲<br />\n有返啲成功感 但係Mk都係冇乜點試過拎頭3名<br />\n<br />\n前排Pokken(格鬥game)試玩 用左一晚熟下點玩<br />\n到第二日同女友玩左十局 開頭諗住讓下佢教佢點玩<br />\n點知到最後俾佢sm 我剩係贏得兩局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好彩仲未輸到dum手制打爆moon<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84905576e6028ed3252cfc8e52c567980ebcd354","tid":379073,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:13:03.000Z","msg":"樓主正廢西"},{"pid":"ead289c22c475e7f903cd225e720c11e24717e3c","tid":379073,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:15:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主正廢西</blockquote><br />\n我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果唔係點開呢個post呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b1b5942d10e636eca1ba7b87bb9f52185fd182","tid":379073,"uid":115700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:18:36.000Z","msg":"YOU ARE NOT ALONE<br />\n<br />\n打LOL 同槍GAME 都係送頭多<br />\n<br />\n試過打街機<br />\n玩左成年 灣岸 <br />\n之後有朋友新玩 用左一個月 已經勁過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c29b5f3e09a6c9114ae196e6f4fa206095317a9b","tid":379073,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:25:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>YOU ARE NOT ALONE<br />\n<b