aces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 距離安全又有時間俾我瞄<br />\n<br />\n而家splatoon都算係槍game?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手制加體感我覺得好瞄好多 除非對手神走位"},{"pid":"71772bf0ea3a864ac7ca93eed93fc48328e2e8cd","tid":379073,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:08:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打lol肯耐心農下,點都有人carry你掛</blockquote><br />\nFarming我得頭七八分鐘集中得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後戰局就開始會變 我嘅食兵數就會大幅下跌"},{"pid":"3cc044e29bfa0ad5e62adba94cd8fa6ba4fa20ea","tid":379073,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:16:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打lol肯耐心農下,點都有人carry你掛</blockquote><br />\nFarming我得頭七八分鐘集中得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後戰局就開始會變 我嘅食兵數就會大幅下跌</blockquote><br />\n唔會掛,越後期先越簡單食兵喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56308a26093030964789bfb29fbdab2760c4d48b","tid":379073,"uid":117664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:16:53.000Z","msg":"輸得多之後贏果場會更開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f845af70dc6fc5eab80d5b59c6578500bad87a1","tid":379073,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:20:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>打lol肯耐心農下,點都有人carry你掛</blockquote><br />\nFarming我得頭七八分鐘集中得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後戰局就開始會變 我嘅食兵數就會大幅下跌</blockquote><br />\n唔會掛,越後期先越簡單食兵喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇錯 就係越後期我就越唔食兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾frd話過好多次了"},{"pid":"1125ea71534014323ba78cce85e348b7bb3d6ba3","tid":379073,"uid":92203,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/29